OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FBT changes mobile and      
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fbroadband price rise policy
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, BT is abandoning mid-contract price    
OL,6, rises linked to inflation after the    
OL,7, telecoms watchdog Ofcom threatened to  
OL,8, ban the practice.                      
OL,10,FIt has been one of several providers to
OL,11,Ftell customers the cost of their mobile
OL,12,Fand broadband services would increase  
OL,13,Fby inflation plus a fixed percentage.  
OL,15,FBut the regulator said that was        
OL,16,Fconfusing and price rises should be    
OL,17,Fspelt out in "in pounds and pence."    
OL,19,FBT has announced it will introduce that
OL,20,Fchange from summer 2024.               
